---
title: Chicken and Soba Noodle Salad with Snow Peas, Mango, and Garlic-Green Onion Vinaigrette
description: Soba noodles, made with hearty buckwheat flour, make the perfect hot-weather dish. Best served cold, they soak up flavourful vinaigrettes better than any other noodles. For the perfect textural balance, juicy mango is offset by crisp snow peas and crunchy cashews.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-soba-noodle-salad-16a0a218.jpg
